  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink30-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> varaivetir koḷḷār tamar avaṇ maṟuppuḻit tōḻi cevilikku aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink30">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vēppunaṉai yaṉṉa neṭuṅkaṭ kaḷvaṉ</l>
          <l> ṟaṇṇaka maṇṇaḷai niṟaiya nelli</l>
          <l> ṉirumpū vuṟaikku mūraṟkivaḷ</l>
          <l> peruṅkavi ṉiḻappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> The man from the village </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the dark paddy flowers drip [pollen]</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> so that the cool interior earth holes of crabs</l>
          <l rend="indent2">whose eyes are as large as neem buds </l>
          <l rend="indent2">become full:</l>
          <l> What about the fact that she is losing [her] great beauty because of him, mother?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
